Convert to base64: https://hellogreg.github.io/woff2base/

Note:

``` svg
<svg viewBox="0 0 240 80"
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <defs>
    <style type="text/css">
      @import
      url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato|Open+Sans|Oswald|Raleway|Roboto|Indie+Flower|Gamja+Flower');</style>
    <style type="text/css">

      @font-face {
      font-family: Segoe Pro Bold;
      src:
      url("data:application/font-woff;base64,")
      }

    </style>
  </defs>
  <svg viewBox="0 0 200 30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <text y="5" font-family="Segoe Pro Bold">Segoe Pro Bold</text>
    <text y="20">Default</text>
    <text x="100" y="20" font-family="Gamja Flower">Gamja Flower</text>
  </svg>
</svg>
```
